## üõ†Ô∏è Installation
To run this project locally, follow these steps:
1. Clone the repository: git clone https://github.com/your-username/movie-recommendation-system.git
cd movie-recommendation-system
2. Create a virtual environment (optional but recommended): python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows use `venv\Scripts\activate`
3. Install the required packages
4. Download the top_rated_9000_movies_on_TMDB.csv dataset and place it in the root directory of the project.
5. Run the Flask application
6. Run on Localhost
